newsitem.title: DUBAI: PRESS DIGEST - United Arab Emirates - Oct 21.
newsitem.headline: PRESS DIGEST - United Arab Emirates - Oct 21.

text.p: These are some of the leading stories in the United Arab Emirates press on Monday. Reuters has not verified these stories and does not vouch for their accuracy.
- UAE President Sheikh Zaid bin Sultan receives telephone calls from Libyan leader and Kuwaiti crown prince.
- GCC justice ministers open meeting in Oman.
- GCC secretary-general says GCC summit to be held in Qatar on December 7.
- Sheikh Mohammad says Dubai has modern basic infrastructure and developed facilities.
- (Egyptian President Hosni) Mubarak lauds Zayed help to Egypt farming.
